## Component Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
  subgraph Frontend
    Pages[Pages (Home, Login, etc.)]
    Widgets[Widgets]
    Providers[State Management]
    Models[Data Models]
    Pages --> Widgets
    Widgets --> Providers
    Providers --> Models
  end
  subgraph Backend
    Handlers[HTTP Handlers]
    Auth[Authentication]
    Database[Database Layer]
    Middleware[Middleware]
    Utils[Utilities]
    Handlers --> Auth
    Handlers --> Database
    Handlers --> Middleware
    Handlers --> Utils
  end
  subgraph External
    WebTester[Web Tester Service]
    SiteChecker[Site Checker]
    Utils --> WebTester
    Utils --> SiteChecker
  end
```
